text:
I enjoy the quiet ambience and cozy environment here. Good highballs and Japanese whiskey and Japanese bas snacks. Misake makes a good cocktail too.

Revisiting in Jan 2023 and this is still my favourite bar in the Robertson Quay area.

A very quiet place to wind down and chill with friends. The owner was kind and friendly, place was clean and well decorated. The ambience was extremely calming and I will most definitely drop by again!
A chill place to wind down after a party with close friends. Mostly patronised by Japanese but not limited to them. Bottle service available. Their popcorn, pizza and popcorn are all excellent
Bartender Misaki is very friendly woman. Itâ€™s very cozy bar. You can try nice Japanese Whisky there.
Ordered $50 single malt double shots neat but got on the rock instead, then was asked to pour the drink into the shot glass! For the price you pay, would not recommend this place.
